      *
      *
      *  TM had been entering quantities and pressing F2 in program
      *  INVR10 and accounting is saying that they should be positive
      *  amounts.  This program is to correct those entries by
      *  reversing the sign but only for all entries for 2016/11/30.
      *
      *  INVR10 is programmed to allow this type of negative entry and
      *  and Jon said to leave the program "as is" for now.
      *
     H            Y.
     FINVPP10 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C                     READ INVPP10                  50
      *
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           IVDATE    IFEQ 20161130
     C           IVKANS    ANDLT*ZERO
     C           IVKANS    MULT -1        IVKANS
     C                     UPDATINVPP101
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     READ INVPP10                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
